<p>OneQode, the high-performance cloud and network provider, and <a href="https://www.getelements.dev/" target="_blank">Elements</a>, a next-generation server engine for game developers, are pleased to announce a strategic partnership targeted at the game industry.</p>
<p>Under this partnership, OneQode will provide the underlying infrastructure for Elements, supporting the hosting of Elements&#39; upcoming Software as a Service (SaaS) product.</p>
<p>Elements is an all-in-one server engine that equips game developers with tools to introduce connected functionality to their games. Its capabilities include maintaining player account databases, achievements, leaderboards, selling digital goods, integrating non-fungible token capabilities, and creating in-game digital economies.</p>
